It’s coming to the end of 2016 and we’re excited to announce a Christmas/New Year giveaway for our fans! Stand to win $250 and 3 cartons of Red Bull for your upcoming parties by participating in this contest.

1. Like our Page
2. Share with us one person you’re most grateful for in 2016 and why
3. Take a photo with that person along with a can of Red Bull 25% less sugar
4. Post it on our wall or tag us in your post and include the hashtag #redbullmoments
5. Winners will be revealed on 27th December

There are so many things to be grateful for and we want to be there with you in your everyday moments. Here’s wishing you all a wonderful Christmas!
